===Noun===
'''noir''' ''m''

# (Noir''e'') A person whose skin is dark. 
# dark

===Expressions===
* ''[[noir de monde]]'' - full of people
* une  ''[[nuit noire]]'' - a [[night]] with little [[moonlight]].

